        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_pro/scenes/missions/miami/scene_flamingo.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository bd77de97-e398-47be-a948-a88a3da74aed).Image",
        "Description": "47,\rYour target is the famous endurance mechanic, Grace Miller. She is the right hand of Sierra Knox and is responsible for sabotaging rival cars in races.\rOur client, Moses Lee, found out about Grace&apos;s mission and not only undid her work, but asked us to retire her completely.\rHe asked us to make her exit be unnoticable but explosive, to send a message to all those who oppose him.\rBest of luck, 47.",
